Cell["\<\
Original matched-flat control for black-hole graph diagnostics\
\>", "Title"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook uses the original matched-flat convention: radius-threshold \
graph for the curved embedding, direct kNN graph for the matched-flat \
projection. Run cells top to bottom. Use maxRefsPerBin = 5 only for smoke \
tests; use All for final runs.\
\>", "Text"],

